# Spend Bill Gates' Money

This is a simple and fun interactive website where you can simulate spending Bill Gates' fortune. The site lets you buy and sell various luxury items, updating your remaining balance in real-time.

## Features

- Buy and sell from a list of 50 luxury items.
- Real-time balance updates.
- Responsive design for both desktop and mobile.

### Technologies Used

HTML5: Structuring the content of the website.
CSS3: Styling, including custom styles and Bootstrap for layout and responsiveness.
JavaScript: Logic to handle purchases, sales, and balance updates.
Bootstrap: Responsive layouts and modern UI components.